---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="Slide">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="content">
            <p class="quote">
                <span class="quote-content">For ambitious African businesses who want to grow — Aswa is the growth technology partner that turns digital investment into measurable results, because we're accountable to outcomes, not just outputs.</span>
                <span class="source">{ AppConfig.brand_name } Brand Position Statement</span>
            </p>
            <p class="content-title">The Territory we own</p>
            <p>The intersection of strategic thinking, technical execution, and African market knowledge — at a price point that growing businesses can actually afford. No one else occupies this specific corner. It's ours to own.</p>
            <p class="content-title">What we actually sell</p>
            <p>Clients think they buy websites. They don't. They buy outcomes.</p>
            <p class="content-title">Level 1 - What we build</p>
            <p>The Deliverables</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Websites</li>
                <li>Web Applications</li>
                <li>Management Systems</li>
                <li>Ecommerce Platforms</li>
                <li>Branding</li>
                <li>Graphic Design</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="content-title">Level 2 - What clients receive</p>
            <p>The Outcomes</p>
            <ol>
                <li>More leads</li>
                <li>More sales</li>
                <li>Better operations</li>
                <li>Stronger brand presence</li>
                <li>Better customer experience</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="content-title">Level 3 - What we really sell</p>
            <p>Every project, every pixel, every system — one objective. Grow the business.</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Business Growth</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
